NAME: Core package
DESCRIPTION: It contains those dictionary objects that are considered to build the core of the dictionary (e.g. variables, members,…).

NAME: Mapping package
DESCRIPTION: It contains those dictionary objects that are necessary in order to represent the relationship between concepts belongig to different Maintenance agencies.

NAME: Rendering package
DESCRIPTION: It contains those dictionary objects that are used in order to visualize the content of the Data definition package.

NAME: Transformation package
DESCRIPTION: It contains those dictionary objects that are used in order to describe data set transformations in the dictionary.

NAME: Data definition package
DESCRIPTION: It contains those dictionary objects that are utilized in order to define cubes (e.g. frameworks, cube structures, combinations,…).

NAME: Legal references package
DESCRIPTION: It contains those dictionary objects that are necessary in order to provide (legal) references for dictionary objects (e.g. members, cubes,…).
